<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for SmartLang by PixelEvolve AB"
>
  <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    PixelEvolve AB ("we," "our," or "us") operates the SmartLang application.
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information
    when you use our application.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <h3>Information from Shopify</h3>
  <p>When you install our app, we access the following data from your Shopify store:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Store information (name, domain, email, locale settings)</li>
    <li>Product data (titles, descriptions, SEO metadata)</li>
    <li>Collection data (titles and descriptions)</li>
    <li>Navigation menus</li>
    <li>Metaobjects and custom content</li>
    <li>Theme content</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Glossary terms and brand names you configure</li>
    <li>Translation preferences and settings</li>
    <li>Support communications</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Usage Information</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Translation history and statistics</li>
    <li>Feature usage patterns</li>
    <li>Error logs for troubleshooting</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Billing Information</h3>
  <p>Payment processing is handled entirely by Shopify. We do not store credit card numbers or payment details.</p>

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide AI-powered translation services</li>
    <li>Store translations for syncing to your Shopify store</li>
    <li>Protect your brand terms from translation</li>
    <li>Improve our translation quality and app features</li>
    <li>Provide customer support</li>
    <li>Manage your subscription through Shopify's billing system</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>OpenAI:</strong> For AI translation processing. Your content is sent to OpenAI's API for translation. We do not share personally identifiable information with OpenAI. OpenAI's privacy policy applies to this processing.</li>
    <li><strong>Shopify:</strong> As our platform provider for authentication and billing. Shopify's privacy policy applies to data stored on their platform.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Infrastructure Providers</h3>
  <p>We use the following services to host and operate the App:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Fly.io:</strong> Application hosting</li>
    <li><strong>Neon:</strong> Database storage (PostgreSQL)</li>
    <li><strong>Upstash:</strong> Redis caching and job queues</li>
  </ul>
  <p>All providers are selected for their security practices and compliance standards.</p>

  <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Active Accounts:</strong> We retain your data while your App subscription is active</li>
    <li><strong>Uninstallation:</strong> When you uninstall the App, we retain data for 30 days before deletion</li>
    <li><strong>Translations:</strong> Stored translations are deleted upon uninstallation</li>
    <li><strong>Logs:</strong> Error and usage logs are retained for 90 days</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
  <p>
    We implement industry-standard security measures including:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>All data transmission uses HTTPS/TLS encryption</li>
    <li>Database access is restricted and encrypted</li>
    <li>API keys and secrets are stored securely</li>
    <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your stored data</li>
    <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your data</li>
    <li><strong>Export:</strong> Export your translation data</li>
    <li><strong>Object:</strong> Object to data processing</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>8. GDPR Compliance</h2>
  <p>
    For users in the European Economic Area (EEA):
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>We process data based on legitimate business interests and your consent</li>
    <li>You may withdraw consent at any time by uninstalling the App</li>
    <li>You have the right to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    SmartLang is designed for business use and is not intended for children under 16.
    We do not knowingly collect information from children.
  </p>

